   A questionnaire was sent to over 300
 households in the area asking for     
 opinions, and details of shopping and 
 leisure journeys. Just over 100       
 completed questionnaires were returned
 and this is a summary of the findings.
   The first question asked was:-      
       {Do you like living here ?}     
    YES {97%}   NO {1%}  NOT SURE {2%} 
{Reasons given}(if YES)                
  _the house or road I live in     {58}
  _the countryside around          {46}
  _friendly people                 {41}
  _clubs & other leisure activities{14}
{Reasons given}(if N0)                 
  _too quiet, nothing to do        { 1}
{Other typical comments made were:}    
 "Family are local, I was born here."  
 "Good access to London and the coast."
 "A gentle pace of life here."         
 "Near to my place of work."           
 "It is a pretty village."
